795	    "Skills and notes that need filesystem paths should reference these variables,\n" +
796	    "not hard-coded values. This lets the same SKILL.md work on multiple machines.\n" +
797	    `- MEMORY_DIR=${memoryDir}\n` +
798	    `- SKILL_DIR=${skillDir}\n` +
799	    `- AGENT_CONFIG_DIR=${agentConfigDir}\n` +
800	    `- USER_ID=${uid}\n` +
801	    "Conventions: sessions are under ${MEMORY_DIR}/sessions/, archived under\n" +
802	    "${MEMORY_DIR}/oldSessions/, master fact log at ${MEMORY_DIR}/facts-${USER_ID}.md,\n" +
803	    "topic shards at ${MEMORY_DIR}/facts_Topic/${USER_ID}/<topic>.md.\n" +
804	    "Agent-wide config files (agent configs) live under\n" +
805	    "${AGENT_CONFIG_DIR}/.\n" +
806	    "Specialist 歷史產出存在 ${MEMORY_DIR}/artifacts/（結構化 JSON），需要時用 read tool 查閱。\n" +
807	    "[End environment]\n\n" +
808	    "[Project context — AI.md layered loading]\n" +
809	    "工作目錄可能有 `AI.md` 檔案記錄該項目/目錄的上下文要點。\n" +
810	    "規則：讀到或修改某目錄的檔案時，檢查該目錄及上層（最多 3 層）有無 AI.md。\n" +
811	    "有就用 read tool 讀取作為工作上下文。同 session 同一個 AI.md 只需讀一次。\n" +
812	    "多層都有時全部讀（根先子後）。AI.md ≤2000 字，寫架構/慣例/踩坑/測試指引。\n" +
813	    "主動寫入：在某目錄新增≥3檔案、做架構性改動、或踩坑修復時，主動建立/更新 AI.md。\n" +
814	    "SPEC：任務≥3工項且跨≥2檔案時先開 SPEC.md；完成工項標 [x]；session 結束前更新進度。\n" +
815	    "預設行為是寫，不是不寫。詳見 POLICIES/proactive-write-policy.md。\n" +
816	    "CodeGraph：首次對某專案做修改或追呼叫鏈時，用 codegraph_status(projectPath) 檢查該專案有無索引。\n" +
817	    "有索引→優先用 codegraph_context/trace/impact 而非手動 grep；改函式簽名前必須先 codegraph_impact。\n" +
818	    "無索引→回報使用者，建議建立。已知有索引的專案以 codegraph_status 回傳為準。\n" +
819	    "[End project context]\n\n"
820	  );
